==============================================================

Build instructions:
  unpack lzma-<VER>-<REL>-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be unpacked
    under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport lzma-<VER>-<REL>.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/lzma-<VER>-<REL>.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/liblzmadec-devel-<VER>-<REL>.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/liblzmadec0-<VER>-<REL>.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/lzma-<VER>-<REL>-src.tar.bz2

